  United States DOJ Drug Enforcement Administration, 2008, webpage:
  [http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/concern/cocaine.html DEA-cocaine] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622214514/http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/concern/cocaine.html |date=2008-06-22 }}.</ref><ref name="Cr90">
  "Life or Meth – CRACK OF THE 90'S",
  Salt Lake City Police Department, Utah, 2008, PDF file:
  [http://www.ci.slc.ut.us/police/pdf/methlife.pdf Methlife-PDF] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071031024458/http://www.ci.slc.ut.us/police/pdf/methlife.pdf |date=October 31, 2007 }}.
</ref>。它的最初作用是釋放大量的[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]，<ref name="AMCcrac">{{cite web|first=Jeremy|last=Arias|website=A.M. Costa Rica|date=July 2008|url=http://www.amcostarica.com/071808.htm|title=Crack rocks offer a short but intense high to smokers|access-date=2020-10-22|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225942/http://www.amcostarica.com/071808.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>一種引起興奮感的大腦化學物質。高峰通常持續5-10分鐘，<ref name="AMCcrac">{{cite web|first=Jeremy|last=Arias|website=A.M. Costa Rica|date=July 2008|url=http://www.amcostarica.com/071808.htm|title=Crack rocks offer a short but intense high to smokers}}</ref><ref name=DEAC/>之後，大腦中的多巴胺水平驟降，使用戶感到沮喪和低落。<ref name="AMCcrac">{{cite web|first=Jeremy|last=Arias|website=A.M. Costa Rica|date=July 2008|url=http://www.amcostarica.com/071808.htm|title=Crack rocks offer a short but intense high to smokers}}</ref>當（粉狀）古柯鹼溶解並注射後，進入血液的吸收速度至少與吸食快克時的藥物吸收速度一樣快<ref name=DEAC/>，並且可能會出現類似的欣快感。

==不良影響==
由於快克是一種[[非法藥物|非法藥物]]，因此使用者可能會食用到不純或偽造的藥物，這可能帶來額外的健康風險。<ref>{{cite news|first=Scott|last=Hesketh|url=https://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/latest-news/benzocaine-crack-scam-nets-drug-18238984|title=Benzocaine 'crack' scam nets drug dealers massive profits|newspaper=[[Daily_Star_(United_Kingdom)|Daily Star]]|date=22 August 2010|accessdate=17 June 2020|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410093642/https://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/latest-news/benzocaine-crack-scam-nets-drug-18238984|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===生理===
古柯鹼的短期生理效應包括<ref name=DEAC/>血管收縮、瞳孔擴大以及體溫、心率和血壓升高。一些古柯鹼使用者表示有躁動、煩躁和焦慮的感覺。在極少數情況下，首次使用古柯鹼可能會導致[[猝死|猝死]]或不可預見的意外發生。<ref name=DEAC/>古柯鹼相關的死亡通常是由於[[心臟驟停|心臟驟停]]或[[癲癇|癲癇]]發作繼之呼吸驟停而死亡。像其他形式的古柯鹼一樣，吸食會增加[[心率|心率]]<ref name=PP/>和[[血壓|血壓]]，從而導致長期的[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]。一些研究表明，與其他服用古柯鹼的方法相比，吸食快克或[[游離鹼|游離鹼]]的古柯鹼具有更多的健康風險。這些問題中的許多問題都與甲基乙炔嘧啶的釋放及其對[[心臟|心臟]]、<ref name="PP">{{cite journal|first1=Karl|last1=Scheidweiler|first2=Mark A.|last2=Plessinger|first3=Jalil|last3=Shojaie|first4=Ronald W.|last4=Wood|first5=Tai C.|last5=Kwong|title=Pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of methylecgonidine, a crack cocaine pyrolyzate|journal=[[Journal_of_Pharmacology_and_Experimental_Therapeutics|Journal of Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics]]|publisher=[[American_Society_for_Pharmacology_and_Experimental_Therapeutics|American Society for Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics]]|location=Rockville, Maryland|volume=307|issue=3|pages=1179–1187|year=2003|pmid=14561847|doi=10.1124/jpet.103.055434|url=http://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/b70c/b72a01c30205621d07ca2c667b8b19894ce1.pdf|access-date=2020-11-05|archive-date=2019-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190303143332/http://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/b70c/b72a01c30205621d07ca2c667b8b19894ce1.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[肺|肺]]、<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Yang Y, Ke Q, Cai J, Xiao YF, Morgan JP |title=Evidence for cocaine and methylecgonidine stimulation of M(2) muscarinic receptors in cultured human embryonic lung cells |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-pharmacology_2001-01_132_2/page/451 |journal=[[British_Journal_of_Pharmacology|British Journal of Pharmacology]] |volume=132 |issue=2 |pages=451–460 |year=2001 |pmid=11159694 |doi=10.1038/sj.bjp.0703819 |pmc=1572570}}</ref>和[[肝臟|肝臟]]<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Fandiño AS, Toennes SW, Kauert GF |year=2002 |title=Studies on hydrolytic and oxidative metabolic pathways of anhydroecgonine methyl ester (methylecgonidine) using microsomal preparations from rat organs |journal=[[Chemical_Research_in_Toxicology|Chemical Research in Toxicology]] |volume=15 |issue=12 |pages=1543–1548 |doi=10.1021/tx0255828 |pmid=12482236}}<!--|accessdate=2008-02-24--></ref>的影響有關。

===吸食過量===
使用者的典型反應是要再次注射該藥，但是，大腦中的[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]水平需要很長時間才能自我補充，每次吸食都會導致欣快感逐漸降低。<ref name=AMCcrac/>但是，一個人可能會在不睡覺的情況下過量吸食三天或更長時間。<ref name=Cr90/>

過量吸食古柯鹼，在此期間反复服用高劑量的毒品，會導致煩躁、不安和偏執狂。<ref name=DEAC/>這可能會導致全面的偏執性精神病，使個人失去與現實的聯繫並發生幻聽。<ref name=DEAC/>

大量的古柯鹼（幾百毫克或更多）可以增加使用者的欣快感，但也可能導致異常、不穩定和暴力行為。<ref name=DEAC/>大量服用可引起[[震顫|震顫]]、[[眩暈|眩暈]]、肌肉抽搐、[[偏執狂|偏執狂]]，或反复服用則可能引起類似於[[苯丙胺|苯丙胺]]中毒的毒性反應。<ref name=DEAC/>

